{"tid":2048111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Facebook不標示特朗普言論違規引發員工罷工","createTime":"2020-06-02T14:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T14:52:14.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"64cf62a4ba51f3b74dab682b6813d61f39b2ff95","tid":2048111,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國黑人男子弗洛伊德懷疑被警員跪頸致死，觸發全國多個城市示威，同時引發搶掠及警民衝突。總統特朗普在社交網絡回應事件的帖文，被指是宣揚暴力，但Facebook認為有關言論沒有違規，引起員工不滿。<br />\n<br />\n美國財經頻道CNBC報道，多達600名Facebook員工周一參加「遠端罷工」，以宣示對公司創辦人朱克伯格在今次事件立場的不滿，亦有員工決定離職，以表明自己不同意公司的用戶言論規管政策。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普日前在Twitter及Facebook發表文章，稱參與示威的民眾是暴徒，又說「一旦發生搶掠就是開槍之時」。Twitter指特朗普的言論是宣揚暴力，決定將帖文隱藏並加上警告；朱克伯格則表示他不贊同特朗普的言論，但認為有關言論沒違規。<br />\n<br />\n這個決定引起Facebook員工不滿，於是在周一發動罷工，由於現時員工因應疫情在家中遙距工作，因此罷工以遠端方式舉行，其間參加者離開電腦，並在Twitter發帖文公布自己正在罷工。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述參加者指，多達600人參加今次罷工，又指朱克伯格會在周二與員工舉行大會討論事件。Facebook發言人回應傳媒查詢是否舉行大會時，則表示不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n發言人重申，公司了解包括非裔族群現時所感受到的痛苦，強調公司鼓勵員工就與高層的分歧發聲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=393050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393050&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=024443f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393050&h=15201343\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=393050</a>"},{"pid":"32c7f6b581d57440596e48ae4eb6e74288fa2ff7","tid":2048111,"uid":215794,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:37:37.000Z","msg":"侵：又唔係twitter罷工 驚閪？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e3836275120ea39ec7a69061d9119dcb7ba92c","tid":2048111,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"睇呢個<br />\n<br />\n[文宣圖] Protest like HongKonger<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2048086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2048086</a>"},{"pid":"49a7dc5d275b9dc9331fd5408278baa9f34830a8","tid":2048111,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"全世界進入價值觀戰爭"},{"pid":"fa5b422c00f4f17cc048194272d18f59e2c16808","tid":2048111,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c8a8f37ec2c485c30527a5d8a6bd135388ba2f","tid":2048111,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"民間怨氣越來越大，侵連任根本已經冇得救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4f3707633ebda2d5cd02447124daf9c135f93b","tid":2048111,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"班左膠真係好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2916541125f4419892cdb73855273e00f9888c86","tid":2048111,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:47:26.000Z","msg":"罷工既有幾多係支那人？"},{"pid":"e5e3de8dc50087dee42260b549df2768e3ec6150","tid":2048111,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"facebook 已經夠奶共架啦"},{"pid":"27862031833c7b58f34bd089f2be5eb21b5525dc","tid":2048111,"uid":193788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:52:14.000Z","msg":"fb審查香港個陣唔出聲<br />\n而家扮乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}